# User-provided CAD resource files (SHX fonts, PAT patterns, LIN linetypes)
# These files are not redistributable and must be provided by the user.
YiCAD/support/fonts/*
!YiCAD/support/fonts/.gitkeep
!YiCAD/support/fonts/README.md

YiCAD/support/patterns/*
!YiCAD/support/patterns/.gitkeep
!YiCAD/support/patterns/README.md

YiCAD/support/linetypes/*
!YiCAD/support/linetypes/.gitkeep
!YiCAD/support/linetypes/README.md

# CMake presets
CMakeUserPresets.json

